      <title>中国经济复苏助力第三季度业绩，亚洲表现最佳</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/wild-swings-in-asian-markets-point-at-more-volatility-to-come</link>
      <description><![CDATA[过去三个月，亚洲资产大幅波动，受到一系列划时代事件的冲击，最终导致中国出台大规模刺激政策，并推动该地区股市成为全球领头羊。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/wild-swings-in-asian-markets-point-at-more-volatility-to-come</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 01:29:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
